  }, "is on my GitHub"), "."), mdx("h2", null, "Physical Design"), mdx("p", null, "Most of the project as focused on the form factor of a human-computer knob\ninterface. I decided three knobs would be useful without being too bulky. I\nwanted a feeling of high quality and solidity, with intuitive purpose."), mdx("p", null, mdx("span", {
